---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="联系 & 加入我们 - rrxr.xyz">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-8">联系 & 加入我们</h1>
  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">联系方式</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-2">邮箱: your_email@example.com</p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">电话: +86 123 4567 8900</p>
  </section>
  <section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">社交媒体链接</h2>
    <ul class="flex space-x-4">
      <li><a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline">微信</a></li>
      <li><a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline">小红书</a></li>
      <li><a href="#" class="text-primary hover:underline">抖音</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">加入共创（合作/学习小组）</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">如果您对合作或加入学习小组感兴趣，请填写以下表单：</p>
    <form class="mt-4 p-6 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-card">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <label for="name" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2">姓名:</label>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline" placeholder="您的姓名">
      </div>
      <div class="mb-4">
        <label for="email" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2">邮箱:</label>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline" placeholder="您的邮箱">
      </div>
      <div class="mb-6">
        <label for="message" class="block text-gray-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2">消息:</label>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" class="shadow appearance-none border rounded w-full py-2 px-3 text-gray-700 leading-tight focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline" placeholder="您的消息"></textarea>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <button type="submit" class="bg-primary hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-xl focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline">发送</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </section>
</Layout>

